{"tid":2077364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"神秘人跟蹤黎智英八日 警首截查","createTime":"2020-06-24T08:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T09:01:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb9553431ebdeeabcd800b4870c0d48d554190f","tid":2077364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:35:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/CXNC3NYUCMZGSNWAEKBERUY2T4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FCXNC3NYUCMZGSNWAEKBERUY2T4%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=5f781e28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FCXNC3NYUCMZGSNWAEKBERUY2T4%2F&h=b9e2fe69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/CXNC3NYUCMZGSNWAEKBERUY2T4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n神秘人跟蹤黎智英八日 警首截查<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】壹傳媒創辦人黎智英昨連續第八日被多名神秘人無間斷跟蹤，涉事可疑車輛更增至三部，惟有跟蹤者「甩轆」，誤以為黎要上庭，駕車往東區法院外兜截，結果撲空。嘉道理道黎宅附近更有居民發現可疑車輛報警，結果多名警員到場截查，是八日來首次有警員調查跟蹤人士。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨約6時，何文田嘉道理道黎宅外，停泊三部可疑七人車，除了連日來出現的白色七人車（車牌US 8045）及黑色七人車（UY 2495）外，另一部日前曾經出現的白色七人車（VE 1058）亦再次在場。其後黎智英由大宅乘座駕返回將軍澳工業邨《蘋果日報》大樓，兩部黑白七人車前後緊隨，抵埗後停在大樓外監視。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BD2HvtS1GQ22JsnIPPTMUKqXPX0=/802x599/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O2SVVS7N7CYG7JREU425OIASGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBD2HvtS1GQ22JsnIPPTMUKqXPX0%3D%2F802x599%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO2SVVS7N7CYG7JREU425OIASGI.jpg&h=c78b143f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數名警員搜查連日跟蹤黎智英的可疑車輛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n封路搜車半小時<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：刑事案法官絕非特首指派<br />\n<br />\n至中午時分，黎智英的座駕駛離大樓，兩部七人車尾隨但「跟甩」。。。。。該車及黑色七人車其後返回黎宅外繼續守候黎智英。<br />\n<br />\n下午近4時，一名居於嘉道理道的外籍人士報警，指發現白色七人車US 8045出現。。。。隨即封鎖一段路，搜查三名神秘男的背囊及車輛，約半小時後要求白色七人車離開，惟事後該白色車再次返回現場，未有再離開。"},{"pid":"d585c91d7770f1df71678b1578eef911ecdd68c0","tid":2077364,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:50:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=072d02df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"aeaea35f15ac6b4ddff9cd55ee534fbe75777c9f","tid":2077364,"uid":36573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"查自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a0347cee669130ba98d0014d518ec411c3cde4","tid":2077364,"uid":243677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c2cca4e6f8c407cdb2db31c2f9fdc5b945920d","tid":2077364,"uid":121197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:57:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母自己友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9834de24c96036ff229c057c8397359a0abaad51","tid":2077364,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"你咩team呀"}]}